snippet.title: Super "Dirty" Craig Ferguson with Actresses on The Late Show 2021
snippet.description:
The Late Show with Craig Ferguson was something truly special. You could try to explain it, but it's something you just had to watch.  There were skits. There were puppets. There was musical intros. There was a robot skeleton. There was not a real (tootsie-fruitsie) horse. With a rip of the prepared questions, there was the best interviews in late night television.  It was truly not like any other late night show.

Please Help Subscribe The Late Show Channels: https://bit.ly/2MLBeEP
